{"tid":1417950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 香港怒吼 林鄭攬炒","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8a4d3194118f34cad6e1e34f212edadc63f12a","tid":1417950,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67575565_10157914801782448_3921390258909872128_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_eui2=AeELk0JZ50kE9UHkjxtcVFVu77JRYE1sRTFZq2p3lSXwuJhWNer-c82-8Kcy6khGBtMH4gEm6ReJatL1oR4X6y2YquQgCEGebsMT0SRHDQN0wg&amp;_nc_oc=AQmpDxC4MxpgozbJO1hYkYHrsQqm0u00qtofZgH1ta1PJ6g-QJmo5m7mvd_xrjrzUKk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=dc6f8334952e79246027e48a2e236e65&amp;oe=5DD3B985\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67575565_10157914801782448_3921390258909872128_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_eui2%3DAeELk0JZ50kE9UHkjxtcVFVu77JRYE1sRTFZq2p3lSXwuJhWNer-c82-8Kcy6khGBtMH4gEm6ReJatL1oR4X6y2YquQgCEGebsMT0SRHDQN0wg%26_nc_oc%3DAQmpDxC4MxpgozbJO1hYkYHrsQqm0u00qtofZgH1ta1PJ6g-QJmo5m7mvd_xrjrzUKk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Ddc6f8334952e79246027e48a2e236e65%26oe%3D5DD3B985&h=aff9caec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f81a574713571007943ef7cbe6c805adff0d620","tid":1417950,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"【#A1頭條】香港人堅持為自由跟極權抗爭，昨日「和理非」全面進場，並發動回歸以來首次全城罷工、罷市、罷課及不合作運動，七區同時舉行罷工集會，但特首林鄭月娥繼續無視市民訴求，昨晨「復工」對傳媒指斥有極端分子已令事件變質，又形容玉石俱焚做法將香港推上不歸路。林鄭漠視民意升級，令大罷工未竟全功，加上警方連日濫暴情況失控，昨午開始多區爆發堵路及包圍警署，以表達對政權的強烈憤怒，結果催淚彈遍地開花，惟抗爭者只見眼前路拒絕撤退。林鄭政權推卸責任再諉過市民，勢跟全港市民攬炒同歸於盡。"}]}